Contributions
=============

Contributions from anyone are more than welcome! This may include opening
`issues <https://github.com/ArcasProject/Arcas/issues>`_, communicating ideas,
implementing new features such as expanding the search fields and the results set.
We would love to recieve new pull requests from you.

Here's a guide to starting a contribution:

Fork, then clone the repo::

    git clone git@github.com:your-username/Arcas.git

Make sure the tests pass::

    pytest tests

We encourage the use of coverage, enusring all aspects of the code are tested::

    py.test --cov=arcas tests/

Add tests for your change. Make your change and make the tests pass.
Please update the documentation too, and ensure doctests pass. Push to your fork
and submit a pull request.

We look forward to your contributions!